clk_wiz_80/
	Clock wizard ip which generates 80Mhz clock.

vio_0/
	Contains the vio connections.

ila_uarts/
	Contains ila for the serial (ila 2) and debug (ila 1).

ila_dram/
	contains ila to check the dram signals

ddr4_0/
	This is the Dram controller ip being used
Incase you are using any other ip's such as DRAM, Ethernet (NIC) etc., add them in this directory.
